reviewText: Didn't care for post grad.  thought I would try like bundles to try new movies. Price is important too. suggestive is good too
A bit sappy -- but at times that is just the ticket! That I got two and at a reasonable price was the reason I bought it,  and I am not at all sorry I made this purchase.

I loved the First Daughter movie but the Post Grad "not so much". This comes on two separate discs but neither has any kind of picture to mark which movie is on the disc. I was hoping these were sold to kind of blend in the stories together but they are totally different stories so I'm not sure why they were sold together. However, these are fun to watch and provide some "low cost" entertainment. Seller shipped quickly and packaged it well.

I really enjoyed the movie First daughter, it was clean and I loved the story line. The characters did a good job with their parts. The other movie Post Grad was not as clean and I didn't enjoy it as much.
First daughter is great. Post grad not worth watching.
Good Communications.  Great Product.  Quick Service.  Rated AAA+++.  Thank You.  BEG
